The Ultimate Hotel for Both Leisure and Business Goers

WHO VISIT THE FINE CITY OF INDIANAPOLIS

The Woods hotel, located in the very heart of Indianapolis is a welcoming retreat for either people traveling across the country or businessmen, visiting our Rustbelt state for some commercial affairs. Here, we always make sure that you will have any of your needs satisfied, be it a comfortable hotel room with a strong WiFi signal and a diligent room service, a dining and lounge zone or any additional amenities a traveller might want… Read more Read more

FREE WIFI

Because both businessmen and travelers need to access the Internet anywhere!

ROOM SERVICE

Enjoy a full-blown room service, enhanced by an option to order food and beverages!

FREE PARKING LOTS

Book a suite and the parking lot will be yours, free of any additional charge!

EARLY CHECK-IN, LATE CHECK-OUT

More flexible than ever, made with our guests’ comfort and timing in mind…

COMFORTABLE STANDARD ROOMS & HIGH-END SUITES

Woods Hotel has 35 elegantly furnished and air conditioned classic rooms, which will be a perfect pick both for business and leisure travelers…

PREMIUM SUITE

Enjoy our classic suites with all the elegancy and comfort that its interior has… It features such essentials as a flat-screen 45″ TV, WiFi and 2 bathrooms with a living room and 2 bedrooms…

Only 5 rooms are available

Breakfast included

Price does not include VAT & services fee

FAMILY ROOM

DINING & BAR

Taste our trademark cocktails & enjoy a truly unique culinary experience…

As the sun sets and the sky turns purple, we celebrate the violet hour and the end of the day before welcoming the start of the night.

That’s correct!We’re so determined to make your experience at our hotel a charm, that we’d love to provide you with a courtesy airport shuttle if you book with us!

item.content:encoded:
THE WOODS HOTEL

While the Woods Hotel is neither the oldest nor the biggest one in Indianapolis or Indiana, we’ve got our own considerably long history of upholding a benchmark level of quality.

Our biggest advantage over other hotels in the city is our balanced approach. With just 35 rooms, we’re a quiet place to stay at.

4 different types of rooms from singles to suites offer a variety of choice, just as much as our excellent dining & our lobby bar…

Additional services and amenities, on par with reasonable prices, make us stand out and win over both Indiana visiting tourists and businessmen on a go…

JUST A FEW REASONS TO CHOOSE THE WOODS HOTEL WHILE STAYING IN INDIANA…

FREE WIFI

Because both businessmen and travelers need to access the Internet anywhere!

ROOM SERVICE

Enjoy a full-blown room service, enhanced by an option to order food and beverages!

FREE PARKING LOTS

Book a suite and the parking lot will be yours, free of any additional charge!

EARLY CHECK-IN, LATE CHECK-OUT

More flexible than ever, made with our guests’ comfort and timing in mind…

GUEST REVIEWS

As a businessman, who travels all year long I can say that this hotel has everything that a man like me may need.

Kurt SmithSATISFIED CUSTOMER

When i and my family were touring the Midwest last summer, we planned to stay in Indianapolis for a while.

Lyndon JohnsonSATISFIED CUSTOMER

I’ve been to a lot of Rustbelt’s hotels in the last few years and this one is definitely one of the best ones.

Eleonora GiovanardiSATISFIED CUSTOMER

RATED WITH 4 STARS BY

SEE OUR HOTEL’S BLOG FOR SPECIAL OFFERS, NEWS & MORE!

item.title: Bar-woods
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
DINING & BAR

While you’ll be staying at our hotel, you will be able to enjoy our exquisite food menu available both at our lobby restaurant and a summer terrace, just as well as order menu items upstairs, as a part of our room service. We offer both meat & fish dishes and vegetarian menu items…

On par with our two restaurants, we also have a lobby bar, which features an extensive Beverages, Spirits and Wines Menu of its own… Try not to get tangled within dozens of miscellaneous cocktails, alcoholic drinks and different wines that we have there!

MAIN COURSES MENU

Taste our trademark cocktails & enjoy a truly unique culinary experience…

As the sun sets and the sky turns purple, we celebrate the violet hour and the end of the day before welcoming the start of the night.
  • Crumbed whiting
    $25.00Fresh local baby whiting fillets in a sesame and parsley crumb s/w chips salad lemon
  • Chicken Parmagiana
    $20.00Chicken Surf & Turf $31 Char grilled garlic chicken breast fillet topped
  • Gluten Free Surf & Turf
    $18.00Char grilled Scotch fillet 300gm topped with a garlic seafood sauce
  • Asian noodle salad
    $30.00Julliene veggies & rice noodles with mint coriander & cashew nuts nestled

DESSERTS MENU

$6.50

Blackcurrant & limoncello compote, crunchy spiced crumble & lemon zest

ORGANIC YOGHURT PANNA COTTA

$5.50

Served with whipped crème fraîche, fresh orange & pomegranate

JAMIES FAVORITE ORANGE BLOSSOM POLENTA CAKE

$5.50

The classic Italian dessert with vin santo, chocolate shavings & orange zest

VIN SANO TIRAMISU

DRINKS MENU

  • Mint Chocolate Grasshopper
    $25.00crème de menthe | crème de cacao | stoli | ice cream
  • Strawberry Mai Tai
    $15.00Strawberry & captain morgan topped with myers rum
  • Fruit Patch
    $15.00A sweet combination of strawberry, mango, rum
  • French Cosmopolitan
    $24.00grey goose | cointreau | cranberry juice
  • Caramel Apple
    $24.00ketel one | sour apple schnapps | sweet & sour
  • Passionate Berry
    $24.00passion fruit | raspberry | vodka | whipped cream
  • The Margaret
    $26.00champagne | vodka | lemon | amaretto
  • The Roslynn
    $26.00champagne | freshly squeezed lemon and orange juice
  • The Julia
    $30.00rose champagne | st germain | soda water
DOWNLOAD THE FULL MENU

item.title: Rooms-woods
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
ROOMS & SUITES

While our hotel has a standard set of the room types, there’s absolutely nothing standard about them! Each single room, double or family room, each suite we offer is enhanced with a little extra of its own!

The intricate and elegant, but at the same time comfortable interior and exterior of the hotel make your stay here a blast! Additionally, all the amenities that we have, hotel-wide WiFI & our incredible eat & drink venues will be a cherry on the top!

SINGLE ROOM WITH BALCONY

This enhanced single room has an advantage of having a great view and a bay window… Enjoy your stay while on a business trip or traveling leisure, with all the amenities and comfort that we have to offer!

DETAILS

Adults: 10

Amenities: Air conditioner, Closet with hangers, Digital Personal Safe, Free high speed Wi-Fi, HD flat-screen TV, Telephone

View: CitySize: 28m²Bed Type: Twin beds

Categories: Deluxe

150 /per night Book a Room Book a Room

PREMIUM SUITE

Enjoy our classic suites with all the elegancy and comfort that its interior has… It features such essentials as a flat-screen 45″ TV, WiFi and 2 bathrooms with a living room and 2 bedrooms…

Only 5 rooms are available

Breakfast included

Price does not include VAT & services fee

Ideal for families of 3 or even 4 people, this room is spacious and comfortable enough for both you and your children to have fun, relax or simply sleep over while traveling… It will make your stay even more pleasant!

item.title: Single Room
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
You can relax and feel at home as all our single rooms are fitted with a spacious semi double bed. Some are also fitted with a desk. Our comfortable single rooms are just the right size if you are travelling alone.
Similar to all the other rooms in the Woods Hotel, the single room is fully equipped with all comforts. Features a bathroom fitted with a walk-in rain shower, minibar, Nespresso coffee machine and flat-screen cable TV.
Electric hot water pot, refrigerator, dryer, table lamp, humidifier, bath, toilet, broadband connection (free), air conditioning are also included.
If you need more services you can ask on the reception for the: Shampoo, hair rinse, body shampoo, toothbrush set, towel, bath towel, slipper, and Japanese tea.
item.excerpt:encoded: You can relax and feel at home as all our single rooms are fitted with a spacious semi double bed.

item.title: Airport Shuttle & Underground Parking
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Free for all visitors except Single Rooms
We know that our hotel's visitors come from different places. But considering that most of them arrive in Indianapolis via the local airport, we wanted to make some extra step for their convenience. As a courtesy service, we're always glad to offer you an airport shuttle service to and from the airport... Additionally, for those of our customers who arrive at the city on their own car, we always offer a secure, underground parking lot, which usually comes at no additional charge (starting with the double room & up). Some extra fees for using the hotel's parking may apply to the visitors staying at our single rooms...

item.title: Room Service & Concierge Service
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Prices depend on the menu items you order
Room service has always been one of the most essential (and popular) services for any hotel. With us being no exception to this practice, we at the Woods Hotel would truly like to be sure that any kind of additional service a customer wants can be easily and timely delivered to them. Besides offering an option to deliver Food & Drinks to your room, we also give you an option to file any additional orders or queries to one of our concierges. Also the list includes same day valet dry cleaning and laundering services...

item.title: SPA & Beauty Centre
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Prices start at $180.00
Having our own SPA & beauty center comes as a great advantage for anyone who's staying with us, as the majority of other hotels in the city do not offer such an additional servicing... Here you'll be able to find a peace of mind at any time, as the SPA center works 24/7. So shake the traveling dust off your shoulders and relax at an hour long massage session... Or, maybe get a new hairdo and a manicure before the evening's dinner... Whatever you choose, be sure that we would never add this as an in-house service, should the quality be any lower that perfect!

item.title: Conference Hall for Business Events
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Prices start at $380.00/hour
Though a majority of our hotel's visitors are families, traveling across the country, many business people visit our city and are staying at our hotel as well. Bearing in mind, that no business event can possibly happen without a place for having a meeting at, we offer you a number of spacious conference rooms for that matter! With all of them having food and beverage catering, included in the renting price, free & speedy WiFi and even complimentary hardware (like TVs, laptops, tablets, and projectors) - we're sure that they will be a perfect fit!http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_58970_v1/wp-admin/edit.php?post_type=mphb_room_service

item.title: Double Room
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Most suitable for couples and the size enables you to relax and feel at home. All rooms are also fitted with a desk, a closet and a washlet. Our Deluxe will make you feel right like at home.
This luxurious room features a bathroom fitted with a walk-in rain shower, Nespresso coffee machine and flat-screen cable TV.
Moreover you will get electric hot water pot, refrigerator, dryer, table lamp, humidifier, bath, toilet, broadband connection (free), air conditioning. Shampoo, hair rinse, body shampoo, toothbrush set, towel, bath towel, slipper, and tea is also for free.
If you need more services you can ask on the reception for the: shaving set, comb, ear buds, anti bacterial inner sole for the slipper, shower cap.
item.excerpt:encoded: Most suitable for couples and the size enables you to relax and feel at home. All rooms are also fitted with a desk, a closet and a washlet.

This is not the first time we choose Woods for our family vacation, it’s just a super impressive hotel! Everything is so special, from room decorations to food. I’m very pleased to be a client of Woods and will surely get there one more time soon!

item.title: Family Room
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
You will have everything you need in our 'basic' family rooms. It immediately feels warm and familiar when you enter. You will have lovely spacious beds, private bathroom (with shower or bath), TV, free WiFi and a modest seat.
The basic rooms offer simplicity in style and the utmost attention has been paid for a pleasant stay. Here you can relax and start and end your day in peace and quiet. Naturally, you can enjoy some extra relaxation in our nice lounge area, with a drink at the bar or in a sunny spot on the terrace.
There is no surcharge for a maximum of two children under 4 years old as long as the existing beds are used. A surcharge of € 10 per night for one child under 2 years old applies should you wish to make use of a baby cot.

item.title: Suite
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
The Suite, which has a separated bedroom and living room that allows for more efficient use of space, is the most optimum place to relax for both business and family guests. It is particularly popular with guests traveling with small children for the extra space it offers.
The dark colors of the interior design create a calm mood that gives the impression of deep rest with even a very short stay. Offers a separate living area, private balcony overlooking the lush garden or lively town, flat screen TV and free WiFi.
Among the exclusive facilities of the Suite, there is a fully equipped business office in the living room equipped with laptop, fax machine and printer (on request), a private bar corner in the living room, an elegant dining area.
Our Suite also enjoys enhanced privileges such as a private check in area, welcome drink upon arrival, enriched fruit basket with water and champagne upon arrival, early check in/late checkout, turn-down service and a farewell gift.

The Woods hotel, located in the very heart of Indianapolis is a welcoming retreat for either people traveling across the country or businessmen, visiting our Rustbelt state for some commercial affairs. ROOM SERVICE

FREE PARKING LOTS

EARLY CHECK-IN, LATE CHECK-OUT

item.title: Amenities
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
HOTEL’S AMENITIES

As a part of our effort to enhance our guest’s stay at our hotel, recently we’ve rolled out a pack of additional hotel services, such as airport shuttle, a business conference hall and much more…

All of these amenities come at a reasonable pricing and with an excellent quality! Be sure, that besides having a nice stay at our place, you will be able to accomplish any additional errands you need…

Airport Shuttle & Underground Parking

Free for all visitors except Single Rooms We know that our hotel’s visitors come from different places. But considering that most of them arrive in Indianapolis via the local airport, we wanted to make some extra step for their convenience. As a courtesy service, we’re always glad to offer you an airport shuttle service to […]

Price: Free

Room Service & Concierge Service

Prices depend on the menu items you order Room service has always been one of the most essential (and popular) services for any hotel. With us being no exception to this practice, we at the Woods Hotel would truly like to be sure that any kind of additional service a customer wants can be easily […]

Price: Free

SPA & Beauty Centre

Prices start at $180.00 Having our own SPA & beauty center comes as a great advantage for anyone who’s staying with us, as the majority of other hotels in the city do not offer such an additional servicing… Here you’ll be able to find a peace of mind at any time, as the SPA center […]

Price: $200 / Per Day / Per Accommodation

Conference Hall for Business Events

Prices start at $380.00/hour Though a majority of our hotel’s visitors are families, traveling across the country, many business people visit our city and are staying at our hotel as well. Bearing in mind, that no business event can possibly happen without a place for having a meeting at, we offer you a number of […]

Price: $390 / Per Day / Per Accommodation

item.title: About us
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
THE WOODS HOTEL

While the Woods Hotel is neither the oldest nor the biggest one in Indianapolis or Indiana, we’ve got our own considerably long history of upholding a benchmark level of quality.

Our biggest advantage over other hotels in the city is our balanced approach. With just 35 rooms, we’re a quiet place to stay at.

4 different types of rooms from singles to suites offer a variety of choice, just as much as our excellent dining & our lobby bar…

Additional services and amenities, on par with reasonable prices, make us stand out and win over both Indiana visiting tourists and businessmen on a go…

JUST A FEW REASONS TO CHOOSE THE WOODS HOTEL WHILE STAYING IN INDIANA…

FREE WIFI

Because both businessmen and travelers need to access the Internet anywhere!

ROOM SERVICE

Enjoy a full-blown room service, enhanced by an option to order food and beverages!

FREE PARKING LOTS

Book a suite and the parking lot will be yours, free of any additional charge!

EARLY CHECK-IN, LATE CHECK-OUT

More flexible than ever, made with our guests’ comfort and timing in mind…

GUEST REVIEWS

As a businessman, who travels all year long I can say that this hotel has everything that a man like me may need.

Kurt SmithSATISFIED CUSTOMER

When i and my family were touring the Midwest last summer, we planned to stay in Indianapolis for a while.

Lyndon JohnsonSATISFIED CUSTOMER

I’ve been to a lot of Rustbelt’s hotels in the last few years and this one is definitely one of the best ones.

Eleonora GiovanardiSATISFIED CUSTOMER

RATED WITH 4 STARS BY

SEE OUR HOTEL’S BLOG FOR SPECIAL OFFERS, NEWS & MORE!

A Definitive Guide to the Best Dining and Drinking Venues in the CityadminMarch 3, 2020 Top Indiana Cities to See Besides Indianapolis and Fort WayneadminMarch 3, 2020 Best Things to See While Staying in IndianapolisadminMarch 3, 2020

item.title: Dining & Bar
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
DINING & BAR

While you’ll be staying at our hotel, you will be able to enjoy our exquisite food menu available both at our lobby restaurant and a summer terrace, just as well as order menu items upstairs, as a part of our room service. We offer both meat & fish dishes and vegetarian menu items…

On par with our two restaurants, we also have a lobby bar, which features an extensive Beverages, Spirits and Wines Menu of its own… Try not to get tangled within dozens of miscellaneous cocktails, alcoholic drinks and different wines that we have there!

MAIN COURSES MENU

Taste our trademark cocktails & enjoy a truly unique culinary experience…

As the sun sets and the sky turns purple, we celebrate the violet hour and the end of the day before welcoming the start of the night.
  • Crumbed whiting
    $25.00Fresh local baby whiting fillets in a sesame and parsley crumb s/w chips salad lemon
  • Chicken Parmagiana
    $20.00Chicken Surf & Turf $31 Char grilled garlic chicken breast fillet topped
  • Gluten Free Surf & Turf
    $18.00Char grilled Scotch fillet 300gm topped with a garlic seafood sauce
  • Asian noodle salad
    $30.00Julliene veggies & rice noodles with mint coriander & cashew nuts nestled
see more see more

DESSERTS MENU

$6.50

Blackcurrant & limoncello compote, crunchy spiced crumble & lemon zest

ORGANIC YOGHURT PANNA COTTA

$5.50

Served with whipped crème fraîche, fresh orange & pomegranate

JAMIES FAVORITE ORANGE BLOSSOM POLENTA CAKE

$5.50

The classic Italian dessert with vin santo, chocolate shavings & orange zest

VIN SANO TIRAMISU

DRINKS MENU

  • Mint Chocolate Grasshopper
    $25.00crème de menthe | crème de cacao | stoli | ice cream
  • Strawberry Mai Tai
    $15.00Strawberry & captain morgan topped with myers rum
  • Fruit Patch
    $15.00A sweet combination of strawberry, mango, rum
  • French Cosmopolitan
    $24.00grey goose | cointreau | cranberry juice
  • Caramel Apple
    $24.00ketel one | sour apple schnapps | sweet & sour
  • Passionate Berry
    $24.00passion fruit | raspberry | vodka | whipped cream
  • The Margaret
    $26.00champagne | vodka | lemon | amaretto
  • The Roslynn
    $26.00champagne | freshly squeezed lemon and orange juice
  • The Julia
    $30.00rose champagne | st germain | soda water
DOWNLOAD THE FULL MENU

item.title: Rooms & Suites
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
ROOMS & SUITES

While our hotel has a standard set of the room types, there’s absolutely nothing standard about them! Each single room, double or family room, each suite we offer is enhanced with a little extra of its own!

The intricate and elegant, but at the same time comfortable interior and exterior of the hotel make your stay here a blast! Additionally, all the amenities that we have, hotel-wide WiFI & our incredible eat & drink venues will be a cherry on the top!

Single Room

You can relax and feel at home as all our single rooms are fitted with a spacious semi double bed.

Details

  • Adults: 2
  • Amenities: Air conditioner, Closet with hangers, Digital Personal Safe, Free high speed Wi-Fi, HD flat-screen TV, Telephone
  • View: City
  • Size: 20m²
  • Bed Type: Single bed
  • Categories: Single

Double Room

Most suitable for couples and the size enables you to relax and feel at home. All rooms are also fitted with a desk, a closet and a washlet.

Details

  • Adults: 2
  • Amenities: Air conditioner, Closet with hangers, Digital Personal Safe, Free high speed Wi-Fi, HD flat-screen TV, Telephone
  • View: City
  • Size: 28m²
  • Bed Type: Double bed
  • Categories: Double

Prices start at: $250 per night


Family Room

You will have everything you need in our ‘basic’ family rooms. It immediately feels warm and familiar when you enter.

Details

  • Adults: 1
  • Amenities: Air conditioner, Closet with hangers, Digital Personal Safe, Free high speed Wi-Fi, HD flat-screen TV, Telephone
  • View: Seaside
  • Size: 28m²
  • Bed Type: Single bed
  • Categories: Honeymoon

Prices start at: $200 per night


Suite

The Suite, which has a separated bedroom and living room that allows for more efficient use of space, is the most optimum place to relax for both business and family guests.

Details

  • Adults: 2
  • Amenities: Air conditioner, Closet with hangers, Digital Personal Safe, Free high speed Wi-Fi, HD flat-screen TV, Telephone
  • View: City
  • Size: 28m²
  • Bed Type: Twin beds
  • Categories: Triple

Prices start at: $250 per night


Premium Suite

The Suite, which has a separated bedroom and living room that allows for more efficient use of space, is the most optimum place to relax for both business and family guests.

Details

  • Adults: 1
  • View: Seaside
  • Size: 35m²
  • Categories: Deluxe

Prices start at: $250 per night


Single room with balcony

You can relax and feel at home as all our single rooms are fitted with a spacious semi double bed.

Details

  • Adults: 10
  • Amenities: Air conditioner, Closet with hangers, Digital Personal Safe, Free high speed Wi-Fi, HD flat-screen TV, Telephone
  • View: City
  • Size: 28m²
  • Bed Type: Twin beds
  • Categories: Deluxe

item.title: Why the Victory Field baseball stadium is so small?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
With its overall history spanning more than 200 years, Indianapolis has a lot of long-established venues, with restaurants, bars, and pubs being at the very top of that list.

We’ve decided to help our Hotel’s guest, who may be visiting the city for the first time in the intricate process of choosing where to eat and drink.

AN ULTIMATE LIST OF THE CITY’S VENUES LOOKS LIKE THIS:

This contender, located at the city’s airport offers a wide choice of organic dishes, with a big emphasis put on vegetarian and gluten free meals…

St. Elmo Steak House

When visiting a typical farming Midwest state like Indiana, enjoying a steak and fried farm vegetables on the side would make perfect sense!

Repeal Restaurant

Being one of the oldest bars & restaurants in the city and serving as a main bootlegging venue during the Prohibition era, this one has a lot of beverages and burgers to offer!

Shapiro’s Delicatessen

A traditionally Italian deli place, also serving some Jewish desserts as well, Shapiro’s is by far the Indy’s top rated bakery of them all!

Scotty’s Brewhouse

Good craft & draft beer, on par with incredible meat burgers and steaks, will make your visit worthwhile and yummy!

So while deciding next time where to go for a lunch try to choose just one of these 5 delicious locations!
